{"tid":2086630,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"新華社：人大常委會全票通過港區國安法　習近平簽署主席令","createTime":"2020-06-30T10:52:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T11:27:40.000Z","uid":149978,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"efe04ec01ce837fe2712b4e6bb79b69ae7082caf","tid":2086630,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:52:05.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】新華社最新報道，全國人大常委會全票通過港區國安法，國家主席習近平簽署主席令予以公布。<br />\n<br />\n報道又指，人大常委會亦表決通過，將港區國安法加入基本法附件三所列的全國性法律。<br />\n<br />\n人大委員長栗戰書說，港區國安法考慮了兩種制度差異和香港具體情況，體現了「懲治極少數，保護大多數」的原則，為維護國家安全、香港長治久安，確保一國兩制事業行穩致遠，提供了法律支撐和保障，這次立法是人心所向，大勢所趨。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=396256\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D396256&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2F1T2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=5c5e20c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D396256&h=a5fcb7ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=396256</a>"},{"pid":"5734bdbd221f5d690b5f921fa8f5028e10ac385e","tid":2086630,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:53:23.000Z","msg":"如果習近平唔簽會點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a0f5b5d7d737ba0b37b2e1a8f1d2c2b8e564ae2","tid":2086630,"uid":39871,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:54:03.000Z","msg":"沒有 沒有 沒有<br />\n通過"},{"pid":"caab51159e3d00dd72116900ce984b790f131164","tid":2086630,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:54:42.000Z","msg":"簽無字天書？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8243306ebde74cfb36de76d8c748f8d578d1f22e","tid":2086630,"uid":361025,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5734bdbd221f5d690b5f921fa8f5028e10ac385e","tid":2086630,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"r